title: Rockettes Bring Tradition of Christmas Spectacular to Holidays
itunes:title: Rockettes Bring Tradition of Christmas Spectacular to Holidays
description:
Radio City Rockettes Alyssa Lemons and Joanna Richardson discuss what's new and exciting from the 2019 Christmas Spectacular Show.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.
